section.section:
"Reinsurance manager" does not include:
an employee of the reinsurer;
a United States manager of the United States branch of an alien reinsurer;
an underwriting manager that, by contract:
manages all or part of the reinsurance operations of the reinsurer;
is under common control with the reinsurer; and
is not compensated based on the volume of premiums written; or
the manager of a group, association, pool, or organization of insurers that:
engages in joint underwriting or joint reinsurance; and
is subject to examination by the insurance regulatory authority of the state where the manager's principal business office is located.
